 Whoa, hi there.

00:17:24.020 --> 00:17:25.820
 What are you doing down there?

00:17:25.820 --> 00:17:27.180
 Oh, dang it.

00:17:27.180 --> 00:17:28.480
 Sorry, sorry.

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:31.660
 You are a bad creature.

00:17:33.140 --> 00:17:33.980
 Look at that.

00:17:33.980 --> 00:17:37.220
 I was wondering what that noise was.

00:17:37.220 --> 00:17:39.620
 Come here, come here, come here.

00:17:39.620 --> 00:17:41.140
 I gotta introduce you to all these folks.

00:17:41.140 --> 00:17:43.500
 Come here, come here.

00:17:43.500 --> 00:17:47.020
 You are not behaving.

00:17:47.020 --> 00:17:50.180
 So this is Shelby.

00:17:50.180 --> 00:17:51.340
 Hi, Shelby.

00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:52.740
 This is Shelby.

00:17:52.740 --> 00:17:53.740
 This is my puppy.

00:17:53.740 --> 00:17:57.060
 I'm trying to keep her out of the cage

00:17:57.060 --> 00:17:59.420
 and let her sit and get by my feet.

00:17:59.420 --> 00:18:00.900
 She's got some chew toys.

