 Chew on your chew toys that I gave you, okay?

00:18:12.940 --> 00:18:15.140
 Let me get through this lecture.

00:18:15.140 --> 00:18:17.260
 Okay, you can get down.

00:18:17.260 --> 00:18:19.340
 Just quit chewing on a...

00:18:19.340 --> 00:18:20.940
 Sorry about that.

00:18:20.940 --> 00:18:23.420
 Dog introduction, dog interruption.

00:18:23.420 --> 00:18:24.940
 I was just hearing chewing noises

00:18:24.940 --> 00:18:26.540
 and I thought I took everything

00:18:26.540 --> 00:18:28.860
 but then there was one pen on the floor.

00:18:28.860 --> 00:18:32.780
 And so the pen, poor pen, meets Mr. Puppy.

